recipes.cookingMethod: Boil spaghetti, saute garlic and pancetta, mix eggs and cheese, combine all ingredients and season with black pepper.

recipes.cookingMethod: Boil galangal, lemongrass, and kaffir lime leaves in chicken broth, add chicken and mushrooms, simmer with coconut milk and fish sauce, garnish with cilantro.
Soak rice noodles, stir fry shrimp and tofu, add noodles and sauce made from tamarind, fish sauce, and palm sugar, add bean sprouts and green onions, serve with lime wedges and crushed peanuts.

Peel and shred green papaya, pound garlic and chili in a mortar and pestle, add fish sauce, lime juice, and palm sugar, toss with papaya, cherry tomatoes, and green beans, garnish with peanuts and dried shrimp.

recipes.cookingMethod: Boil chicken in coconut milk and curry paste, add noodles and top with crispy egg noodles, pickled mustard greens, and red onion, serve with lime wedges and chili oil.
